---
title: Carb Smart Beefy Borscht Inspired Stew with Sour Cream and Chives
description: Filling and hearty is the name of the game with this borscht inspired recipe. Ground beef is stewed with dill-garlic spice blend as well as a melange of traditional borscht veggies like cabbage, potatoes and onions. Finished with a generous of dollop sour cream, your taste buds will be off off and away!
